description:
Evan You, creator of Vue.js talks about the latest Vue 3.0 release. Vue 3.0 is a complete rewrite including many new features and tools, improved developer experience, improved performance and unlocks new capabilities for the Jamstack. 

Learn more about Vue.js: https://twitter.com/vuejs , https://v3.vuejs.org/

Presented by Evan You, Creator and Team Lead for Vue https://twitter.com/youyuxi, https://evanyou.me/

Brought to you by Netlify (netlify.com) - Jamstack Conf Virtual 2020 https://jamstackconf.com
title: JamSnack - What's New in Vue.js
